	   <tr><td colspan=2>Currently, yes it is the last of the quests. However, a recent post from Steve Burke states:<br><br>"I regret that I was unable to complete the implementation of the final quests for the Coldain Shawl before Luclin production began. It's still my intention to implement the remaining segments, but my current workload has forced me to postpone its completion. I hope you'll feel the remaining portion was worth the wait. <br><br>Steve Burke"<br><br>However, the cool thing with these shawls, is that there is an ADDITIONAL stat added to each shawl, as well as, each stat going up by +1.<br><br>For example, the 6th shawl has +6 to everything and has + stamina added. The 7th shawl has +7 to everything and has + sv poison too.<br><br>I imagine, that if these shawls go upto say 10, we probably will end up seeing + str, + sv disease and + sv magic (hopefully), or maybe + agi instead of str. <br><br>Anyways, these are excellent quests and I can't wait to get started on them :)<br>&nbsp;<br>Holmium Elblastee<br>49 Erudite Wiz<br>Torvonnilous</td></tr>
